column5: Open Library is one of my favorite websites!#NewlineYou have the world's classic literature at your fingertips; over a million free eBook titles are available. #NewlineI'll be happy to search the Open Library for you. Please enter an author and/or title#Comma or your topic.#Newline#NewlineOPNLIBBKS#Newline
Let's see what we find in the Open Library.#Newline<think>#Newline<set name="search">opnlib</set>#Newline<set name="searcharg"><star/></set>#Newline<set name="topic"/>#Newline</think>
